config IT8951
	bool "IT8951 e-paper display controller"
	default y
	depends on DT_HAS_ITE_IT8951_ENABLED
	depends on SPI
	help
	  Enable driver for the ITE IT8951 e-paper display controller.
	  The IT8951 is suitable for large reflective e-paper panels such as
	  the E Ink ED103TC2 (10.3-inch, 1872 x 1404, 16 grey levels).
